messages.messageBody:
I agree... My son bought one for me on E-bay... hmm not a good sword...
and I am thinking it was made in the middleeast if I am not mistaken. lol...
so it sits in the bottom of one of my bunks on my sailboat collecting rust I
assume... have not seen it for some times.. lol... But never the less his
heart was in the right place... Nice to know that I have sch an honrable son.
who shows a great interest...
